05/06/2005
STRASBOURG, France -- The 3 July parliamentary elections in Albania represent a window of opportunity for the country's democratic development and EU integration, according to a statement from the Parliamentary Assembly of the Council of Europe (PACE), whose delegation paid a visit to Tirana earlier this month. 
The officials met with political leaders to assess preparations for the vote, stressing that Albania is expected to follow the principles of democratic, free and transparent elections. 
(PACE Web site - 02/06/05)
